name: Youtube blue outline
css:
@-moz-document domain("www.youtube.com")
{
 /* 
    v1.0.1
      Updated to work with youtube premium
    v1.0.1....2
      Just removed unnecessary stuff, and fixed a bug regarding bright theme 
*/
  
  #logo-red-icon-container, #logo-icon-container
  {
    content: url('data:image/png;base64,') !important;
    background-image: none !important;
  }

  html[dark] #logo-icon-container, html[dark] #logo-red-icon-container
  {
    content: url('data:image/png;base64,') !important;
    background-image: none !important;
  }
}
